    "description": "Are you a skilled Surgeon looking for your next big career move? Piramal Pharma in Bhopal offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Piramal Pharma:\nPiramal Pharma is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Piramal Pharma!",
